(113, 1, '2016-07-30 17:27:19', '2016-07-30 17:27:19', 'For nearly 11 months (since March 2015), Descon has focused on reform, screening personnel, strengthening and building management systems to ensure transparency, respect and efficiency for all Descon’s partners – This strategy has been oriented clearly and specially by Board of Management and Board of Directors before.\r\n\r\nAfter the period of reforms mentioned above, Descon has begun participating in the bidding and get more projects; by the following projects Gain Lucky, Vinafco Hau Giang, Descon has got the Huafu Spinning Factory – Phase 2 with 6E and 7E warehouse packages in Thuan Dao Industrial Zone, Ben Luc, Long An with construction time is 05 months.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/phoi-canh-Huafu.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5133" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/phoi-canh-Huafu.jpg" alt="phoi canh Huafu" width="1" height="1" /></a><a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Huafu.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5141" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Huafu.jpg" alt="Huafu" width="1024" height="588" /></a>\r\n\r\nIt’s said that Huafu Spinning Factory is the project marking the return to the market of Descon to implement reforms in recent years with the desire to build up more trust, credibility, transparency, respect, efficiency and safety for all partners and all employees of Descon.', 'DESCON WINS HUAFU SPINNING FACTORY PROJECT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'descon-wins-huafu-spinning-factory-project', '', '', '2016-08-01 16:12:23', '2016-08-01 16:12:23', '', 0, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/?p=113', 0, 'post', '', 0),
