(147, 1, '2016-08-01 15:04:38', '2016-08-01 15:04:38', 'On November 24<sup>th</sup>, 2015, Gain Lucky Vietnam Company Ltd held an inauguration ceremony for Gain Lucky (Vietnam) Textile Factory in Phuoc Dong Industrial Park, Tay Ninh Province.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5069" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/11.jpg" alt="1" width="768" height="512" /></a>\r\n\r\nGain Lucky (Vietnam) Textile factory is invested by Shenzhou International Group Holdings Limited listed in Hong Kong. The project is built on an area of 86 ha in Tay Ninh Province with a total investment of 300 million dollars. Phase 1 of the project was completed and put into operation in late 2014.\r\n\r\nDescon has built phase 2 of the project including: 2 floral print workshop, raw fabric warehouse, finished fabric warehouse and its infrastructure. With the expeditious and urgent progress, after 6 months of construction, Descon has completed the main items and handed over to the owner.\r\n\r\nCurrently, Descon continues to execute some extra items as the investor’s request and be going to finish at early December, 2015.', 'Inauguration ceremony for Gain Lucky (Vietnam) Textile Factory', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'inauguration-ceremony-for-gain-lucky-vietnam-textile-factory', '', '', '2016-08-01 16:13:37', '2016-08-01 16:13:37', '', 0, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/?p=147', 0, 'post', '', 0),
