(152, 1, '2016-08-01 15:06:59', '2016-08-01 15:06:59', 'After buying some new concrete equipment, Equipment department of Descon has hold a training course to use these equipment for Equipment team and site employees.\r\n\r\nThe training program takes place in 10 days from October 10th to October 21st, 2015. The training contents include introduction about machine theory, using of equipment and guidance ofoperating, repairing, maintaining and cleaning with the attendance of over 20 employees of equipment team and technical representative of sites.\r\n\r\nThere are 4 kinds of machine put into this training course: Mini screed, Mini Rake, Ride on power trowel machine and Allen power buggy. These machines will combine together in concrete work to help trowel concrete reach quality and highest efficiency to meet the requirements of a flat, glossy concrete floor with perfect quality. Moreover, these new machines have small size, simple operation and easy to move, so the concrete work on the floor of high - rise building will be also convenient and easier.\r\n\r\nUnder the guidance of 3 technical experts from Ancon Beton, Australia – supplier of equipment for Descon, the training took place very seriously and urgently. Before operating officially on the concrete floor, the participants have learned the theory, how to use and operate each machine. At the beginning, the operation met many difficulties because the users were unfamiliar with machines and its operation. However, with the enthusiastic support of the experts, all trainees have operated these machines smoothly, finished concrete floors of the equipment warehouse area.\r\n\r\nAfter that, from October 19<sup>th</sup> to 21<sup>th</sup>, training activities held at Ministry of Public Security Condominium project’s site. Right here, all equipment will be used into concrete work on the floor of the project.\r\n\r\nThis is considered the most important practicing workshop in the training course, the quality of the concrete flat is the most important result proved the advantage of application of machinery in construction. In the next time, Descon will use these concrete machines in concreting work for flat floor in all the projects to ensure delivering the highest - quality building product to the customers.\r\n\r\nSome photos in the training course:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/4.jpg" alt="4" width="768" height="512" /></a>\r\n\r\nTwo experts come from Australia\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/5.jpg" alt="5" width="768" height="512" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/2.jpg" alt="2" width="768" height="512" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/1.jpg" alt="1" width="768" height="512" /></a>', 'Descon hold a training course for using concrete equipment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'descon-hold-a-training-course-for-using-concrete-equipment', '', '', '2016-08-01 16:14:10', '2016-08-01 16:14:10', '', 0, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/?p=152', 0, 'post', '', 0),
