eight="401" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5024" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2.jpg" alt="2" width="650" height="376" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5025" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3.jpg" alt="3" width="650" height="431" /></a>', 'Khánh thành Nhà máy Royal Foods và Kho lạnh Frescol Nghệ An', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-01 15:10:20', '2016-08-01 15:10:20', '', 154, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/2016/08/01/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(157, 1, '2016-08-01 15:11:12', '2016-08-01 15:11:12', 'After more than 16 months of construction with the strict requirements on quality and construction progress, on September 09<sup>th</sup>, 2015, Royal Foods Nghe An and Frescol cold storage which built by main contractor Descon, was inaugurated in Nam Cam Industrial Park, Nghe An Province.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Khanh-thanh-nha-may.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5022" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Khanh-thanh-nha-may.jpg" alt="Khanh thanh nha may" width="800" height="420" /></a>\r\n\r\nRoyal Food canned fish factory (Three Ladies brand), invested by Royal Foods Nghe An (Thailand), has an area of more than 140.000 m2 and production scale from 60,000 to 100,000 barrels of canned fish per month.\r\n\r\nInvested by Fresh food and cold storage, Frescol Cold Storage is the first largest cold storage of the Northern and Central region with capacity of 13 thousand tons. As scheduled, the storage will begin phase 1 with a capacity of 12,000 tons and frozen 100 - 150 tons /day.\r\n\r\nWith the determination of the Site management in ensuring safety during the project construction, Descon has achieved milestone of 1.2 million man hours free of lost time incident for both projects. On this occasion, Descon also awarded distinctions and reward for individuals well observed labor safety at the project.\r\n\r\nThis result is probably deserved recognition for the efforts of site management team in ensuring safety, progress and quality of the project, motivated Descon continue to achieve higher milestones in the future.\r\n\r\nSome photos of the project:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5023" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1.jpg" alt="1" width="650" height="401" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5024" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2.jpg" alt="2" width="650" height="376" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5025" src="http://descon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3.jpg" alt="3" width="650" height="431" /></a>', 'Opening ceremony of Royal Foods Nghe An Factory and Frescol Cold Storage', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'opening-ceremony-of-royal-foods-nghe-an-factory-and-frescol-cold-storage', '', '', '2016-08-01 16:14:46', '2016-08-01 16:14:46', '', 0, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/?p=157', 0, 'post', '', 0);
