 đến Chủ đầu tư/ Tư vấn nhằm giảm thiểu việc chất lượng không đạt yêu cầu.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Căn cứ vào các thủ tục và hướng dẫn an toàn của công ty để xúc tiến, tạo ra và duy trì môi trường làm việc an toàn.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Tuân thủ các thủ tục ISO của công ty.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Cung cấp chi tiết bảng khối lượng cụ thể các công tác đã thực hiện trình Chỉ huy trưởng thanh toán.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Chi tiết cụ thể hơn sẽ được thảo luận trong buổi phỏng vấn.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Yêu cầu cơ bản:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Tốt nghiệp đại học chính quy chuyên ngành Xây dựng dân dụng và công nghiệp của các Trường ĐH Bách Khoa, ĐH Kiến trúc, ĐH Xây Dựng Hà Nội, ĐH Bách Khoa Đà Nẵng, ĐH Giao Thông Vận Tải, ĐH Sư Phạm Kỹ Thuật TP.HCM và các trường ĐH uy tín khác.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Có ít nhất 1 năm kinh nghiệm ở vị trí tương đương.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Kỹ năng quản lý và tổ chức công việc tốt.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sử dụng tốt phần mềm tin học chuyên ngành.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Giao tiếp và viết tốt bằng cả tiếng Việt và tiếng Anh.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thể / Tư vấn/ Nhà thầu.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;">Thu nhập và phúc lợi:</span></strong></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thu nhập (gồm lương, tiền thưởng và các khoản phụ cấp): Thỏa thuận trong quá trình phỏng vấn.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thưởng hằng năm: đã bao gồm trong Tổng thu nhập đã thỏa thuận.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Tham gia BHXH, BHYT, BHTN theo luật định khi ký kết HĐLĐ chính thức.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Các chế độ khác: Đào tạo, du lịch, bảo hiểm sức khỏe.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Địa điểm làm việc:</strong></span> Theo sự điều động của công ty.</span></h4>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Hồ sơ ứng tuyển:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thư tìm việc.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Mẫu hồ sơ ứng tuyển (tải về tại website <a href="http://www.tanphatlong.com.vn">www.tanphatlong.com.vn</a>)</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sơ yếu lý lịch ghi rõ quá trình học tập, làm việc có ảnh 3x4 cm.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Bản photo bằng cấp chứng chỉ.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Cách thức nộp hồ sơ:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Nộp hồ sơ dự tuyển trực tiếp, gửi bưu điện hoặc gửi email về địa chỉ sau:</span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">BỘ PHẬN NHÂN SỰ - CÔNG TY CỔ PHẦN KỸ THUẬT TÂN PHÁT LONG</span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">634, Đường 34, Khu phố 5, Phường An Phú, Quận 2, TP. HCM</span></em></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Email: <a href="mailto:hr@tanphatlong.com.vn">hr@tanphatlong.com.vn</a></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">ĐT: (084) 08.6281.3454 - 6281.3451 (Ms. Trang - Chuyên viên tuyển dụng).</span></h4>', 'Giám sát thi công', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1035-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:25:31', '2016-09-12 09:25:31', '', 1035, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/1035-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1038, 1, '2016-09-12 09:27:37', '2016-09-12 09:27:37', '<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1032" src="http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/DSC2371-1024x819.jpg" width="840" /></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #205391;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;">Position Summary:</span> Construction Supervisor</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Numbers:</strong></span> 15</span></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;">Job Description:</span></strong></h3>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Make plans, organize and implement the project construction in accordance with budget and progress to meet the demand of Consultant/ Client.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Stay connected with Client/ Consultant and relevant partners to conduct effectively all CSA/MEP works of the project.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Supervise and control the works in tight compliance with the Quanlity Management System, identify all construction risks, evaluate and manage the quality and safety.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Instruct construction teams and sub-contractors to finish their tasks as required by the workload detailed drawings and technical drawings.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Supervise the ongoing tasks before sending supervision requests to the Client/ Consultant in order to minimize risks and bad quality.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Based on safety regulations and instructions, create and maintain a safe working environment.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Comply with the ISO systems of the Company.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Submit a report of completed tasks to the Project Manager.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Other issues are to be discussed in the interview.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Basic Requirement:</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Graduated from public universities on civil engineering and industrial construction major like HCMC University of Technology, HCMC University of Architecture.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Professional management and organization skill.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Good English skills (listening, speaking, writing).</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Problem-solving capability to meet the demand of Clients/ Consultants/ Contractors.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;">Compensation:</span></strong></h4>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Competitive salary package (including net salary, bonuses and allowances): To be discussed.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Annual bonus: Included in agreed Gross income.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Social insurance, Health Insurance, Unemployment Insurance when offer long-term contract.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Other welfares: Training, company vacation, medical insurance.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Work Location:</strong></span> As designated by the company.</span></h4>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Application Form:</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Cover letter.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Application form (download from our website <a href="http://www.tanphatlong.com.vn">www.tanphatlong.com.vn</a>).</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Detailed resume including information on education and experiences + portrait photo (3x4 cm).</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Photocopies of relevant certificates.</span></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">How to apply:</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Apply directly, via post office or send your email to:</span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">HR DEPARTMENT - TAN PHAT LONG ENGINEERING CORPORATION</span></strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Address: 634, Street 34, Quarter 5, An Phu Ward, District 2, HCMC.</span></em></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Email: <a href="mailto:hr@tanphatlong.com.vn">hr@tanphatlong.com.vn</a></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Phone: (084) 08.6281.3454 - 6281.3451 (Ms. Trang - Recruitment Executive).</span></h4>', 'Construction Supervisor', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'construction-supervisor', '', '', '2016-09-13 02:08:07', '2016-09-13 02:08:07', '', 0, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/?post_type=manage-recruitment&#038;p=1038', 0, 'manage-recruitment', '', 0),
(1039, 1, '2016-09-12 09:56:42', '2016-09-12 09:56:42', '<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1032" src="http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/DSC2371-1024x819.jpg" width="840" /></h3>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #205391;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;">Position Summary:</span> Construction Supervisor</span></strong></span></h3>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Numbers:</strong></span> 15</span></h3>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;">Job Description:</span></strong></h3>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Make plans, organize and implement the project construction in accordance with budget and progress to meet the demand of Consultant/ Client.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Stay connected with Client/ Consultant and relevant partners to conduct effectively all CSA/MEP works of the project.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Supervise and control the works in tight compliance with the Quanlity Management System, identify all construction risks, evaluate and manage the quality and safety.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Instruct construction teams and sub-contractors to finish their tasks as required by the workload detailed drawings and technical drawings.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Supervise the ongoing tasks before sending supervision requests to the Client/ Consultant in order to minimize risks and bad quality.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Based on safety regulations and instructions, create and maintain a safe working environment.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Comply with the ISO systems of the Company.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Submit a report of completed tasks to the Project Manager.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Other issues are to be discussed in the interview.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Basic Requirement:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Graduated from public universities on civil engineering and industrial construction major like HCMC University of Technology, HCMC University of Architecture.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Professional management and organization skill.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Good English skills (listening, speaking, writing).</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Problem-solving capability to meet the demand of Clients/ Consultants/ Contractors.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;">Compensation:</span></strong></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Competitive salary package (including net salary, bonuses and allowances): To be discussed.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Annual bonus: Included in agreed Gross income.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Social insurance, Health Insurance, Unemployment Insurance when offer long-term contract.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Other welfares: Training, company vacation, medical insurance.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Work Location:</strong></span> As designated by the company.</span></h4>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Application Form:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Cover letter.</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Application form (download from our website <a href="http://www.tanphatlong.com.vn">www.tanphatlong.com.vn</a>).</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Detailed resume including information on education and experiences + portrait photo (3x4 cm).</span></h4>\n</li>\n 	<li>\n<h4><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Photocopies of relevant certificates.</span></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">How to apply:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Apply directly, via post office or send your email to:</span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">HR DEPARTMENT - TAN PHAT LONG ENGINEERING CORPORATION</span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Address: 634, Street 34, Quarter 5, An Phu Ward, District 2, HCMC.</span></em></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Email: <a href="mailto:hr@tanphatlong.com.vn">hr@tanphatlong.com.vn</a></span></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Phone: (084) 08.6281.3454 - 6281.3451 (Ms. Trang - Recruitment Executive).</span></h4>', 'Construction Supervisor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1038-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:56:42', '2016-09-12 09:56:42', '', 1038, 'http://nhah90.com/tanphatlong/1038-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
